race.comment: TRENT CRIMM (2) is having his first look at this track. Comes here after a last start 4th and beaten 8 lengths (20.63) at Gunnedah. Has never been out of the placings from two starts out of this box. Looks the one to beat on his best form. SILVER REIN (1) turned in a fair run last time from an unfavourable draw finishing fourth by 1.5 lengths (22.84). Leading chance. RAINBOW BLUE (4) turned spotting a big start finishing fourth (23.90) last time in a Grade 5 at The Gardens. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings four times from eight attempts. Expected to feature in the finish. LADY ZAG (6) has to be respected despite coming off a five-and-a-half months break.
